          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Data Consolidation"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Through extensive data cleaning & modeling, we consolidate all your data sources including cloud-based softwares, ERP, sensors, etc, to provide a holistic view of your farm data. REQUEST A CALL"
