          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Actionable Farm Insights"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "From crop management to financial tracking, gain granular insights to make informed decisions. REQUEST A CALL"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Usability"
        },
        {
