    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Gain in-depth Insights into your Farm Business"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "With our detailed pre-built agriculture data analytics dashboard, you will be able to gain crucial insights such as:"
        },
        {
          "t": "img",
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Frame-1000001875-1-elementor-io-optimized-1.webp",
          "w": 185,
          "h": 150,
          "alt": ""
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "With our detailed pre-built agriculture data analytics dashboard, you will be able to gain crucial insights such as:"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "What are your on-going operations and their current status"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Water Consumption for each crop type"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "What was each employee’s productivity to determine labor cost."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Identify reserved and available machinery to plan your next activities."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "What are your most profitable and least profitable crops in each season?"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Budgeted vs Actual cost consumed by each crop during a season to access your financial targets."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Quantity of each resource such as fertilizer, pesticides, etc, were consumed by a crop."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Based on historical data, calculate forecasted yield and compare with actual annual yield."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Forecasted demand for upcoming season to plan your yield accordingly."
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "Speak to Our Experts",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
